author: IGN
description:
Check out the official trailer for Aetherdrift, an upcoming set for Magic: The Gathering built around an interplanar race across the multiverse. 

Aetherdrift releases in both paper and digital on February 14, with prerelease events starting February 7.

title: Magic: The Gathering - Aetherdrift - Official Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Get a look at some creepy first-person gameplay from Dream Cage, the upcoming horror game that puts you in the shoes of a 50-year-old insomniac struggling with sleep paralysis who must grapple with his fears realized before his eyes over five terrifying nights. 

Wishlist it on Steam if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3122170/Dream_Cage/ 

#DreamCage #Gaming #IGN
title: Dream Cage - Exclusive Gameplay Trailer

author: IGN
description:
A new season full of anime is here to check out! A red ranger, a genius animator, and a Holy Grail War are what you can expect this Winter anime season. There's a new season full of anime to check out this Winter like the return of the powerful Sung Jinwoo from Solo Leveling, the beautifully animated Zenshu, and a new full season of Fate/strange Fake. Across Crunchyroll, HIDIVE, Hulu, and Netflix, as well as others, there are a lot of places to enjoy anime at the moment. Don't forget to stick to the end of the video to see the list of Winter anime 2025 available this season. Let us know which 2025 Winter anime you're looking forward to in the comments below!

#IGN #Anime #anime2025
title: New Anime to Watch | Winter 2025

author: IGN
description:
For Honor's new Mongolian Hero, the fierce Khatun, brings Turco-Mongol sabers to the battlefield on January 23. Learn more about the Khatun and the second title update of the Y8S4 during the Warrior’s Den on January 22 at twitch.tv/forhonorgame at 12pm EST. For Honor will be also available for free from January 23 to January 30 on Xbox and PlayStation and from January 23 to February 3 on Ubisoft Connect.

#ForHonor #Khatun #Gaming
title: For Honor - Exclusive Khatun Hero Reveal Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Check out the Sworn release date trailer for the co-op action roguelike developed by Windwalk Games. Players will explore and claim Camelot for their own after the land falls to a compromised Arthur and the Knights of the Round Table. Master abilities from run to run on a quest to overthrow a demented reign. Sworn is launching into Steam Early Access on February 6 for PC (Steam) with a release on PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and Nintendo Switch later in 2025.

#Sworn #Gaming #Games
title: Sworn - Official Release Date Announcement Trailer
